# 17. Testing

## Molecule testing
~~~yml
---
dependency:
  name: galaxy
driver:
  name: docker
platforms:
  - name: instance1
    image: quay.io/centos/centos:stream8
    pre_build_image: true
  - name: instance2
    image: debian:latest
    pre_build_image: true

provisioner:
  name: ansible
verifier:
  name: ansible
~~~

